name: Diethyl Moiré
description:
An encounter with the liminal womb of Totality.

Process: Forged in Hydra, screen captured via OBS Studio, trimmed in Adobe Premiere Pro, then cropped and rendered to 640x480 in Adobe After Effects. 

Played back through a Sony KV-13FM12 via Canopus ADVC-110, with the signal stabilized and enhanced via For.A FA-370. Rescanned via Nikon D7100 donning an Asahi SMC Takumar 1.8/55, interfaced direct to computer via HDMI to Blackmagic Design UltraStudio Recorder 3G and OBS Studio.

Footage edited in Adobe Premiere Pro, then composed, colour graded and rendered in Adobe After Effects and converted with HandBrake.
